  "body": "Closes #12831.\n\nThis breaks many closures (about 10%) that look like this:\n\n```\nlet mut sum = 0;\nf.map(|x| sum += x);\n```\n\nInstead, rewrite them like this:\n\n```\nlet mut sum = 0;\n{\n    let sum_ptr = &mut sum;\n    f.map(|x| *sum_ptr += x);\n}\n```\n\nOr, ideally, switch to RAII- or iterator-like patterns.\n\n[breaking-change]\n\nr? @pnkfelix\n",
